#compdef latencytop
# Documentation: https://manpages.debian.org/testing/latencytop/latencytop.8.en.html
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-19
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# Per the latencytop(8) manpage, the only flag is --unknown; remaining
# positional arguments are process names/identifiers to monitor.
_arguments -s \
  '--unknown[show traces with unknown reasons]' \
  '*:process:_pids'
